    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300124900_5_1955-2013",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "1955-2013",
      "markText": "我们最终的共同目标，是建立一个人与人之间互相包容、互相合作的世界；我们共同享有地球上的一切资源，也在地球上和平共处。",
      "totalCount": 615,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300124900&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=1955&rangeEnd=2013",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/b4c320a0813ab974ag010e05?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=1955&rangeEnd=2013"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300124900_4_1408-1464",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "1408-1464",
      "markText": "历史不会重复，但其内在的发展运行确有其独特的过程。掌握了这一过程，从某种程度上来讲，历史学就会成为最好的未来学。",
      "totalCount": 504,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300124900&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=1408&rangeEnd=1464",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/b4c320a0813ab974ag010e05?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=1408&rangeEnd=1464"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300124900_6_1021-1111",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "1021-1111",
      "markText": "我们求安定，但我们不怕变化，而且愿意直面变化，改造自身。所以，“定中有变，变中有安”，是中国历史发展的基本面貌。就如同百年来的近现代中国，衰极之后还是可以找到出路，一直发展到今天。",
      "totalCount": 480,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300124900&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=1021&rangeEnd=1111",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/b4c320a0813ab974ag010e05?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=1021&rangeEnd=1111"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300124900_3_547-602",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "547-602",
      "markText": "我不在书斋里，我在人中间。 ——许倬云",
      "totalCount": 459,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300124900&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=547&rangeEnd=602",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/b4c320a0813ab974ag010e05?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=547&rangeEnd=602"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300124900_4_607-657",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "607-657",
      "markText": "当下的时代，变化频密，凡事讲求短平快。懂得从历史和他人身上汲取力量、为我所用的人，是真正有智慧的人。",
      "totalCount": 272,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300124900&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=607&rangeEnd=657",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/b4c320a0813ab974ag010e05?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=607&rangeEnd=657"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300124900_7_3698-3761",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "3698-3761",
      "markText": "他认为：当时的苏联以推行马克思主义、社会主义为借口，表面上宣称要谋求人类共同的、永久的福祉，实际上还是发展了旧沙俄的帝国主义。",
      "totalCount": 270,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300124900&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=3698&rangeEnd=3761",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/b4c320a0813ab974ag010e05?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=3698&rangeEnd=3761"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300124900_4_905-948",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "905-948",
      "markText": "我们还谈到了中国传统知识分子赖以安身立命的“横渠四句”，讨论当下的知识分子该如何自处。",
      "totalCount": 256,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300124900&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=905&rangeEnd=948",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/b4c320a0813ab974ag010e05?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=905&rangeEnd=948"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300124900_5_2562-2639",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "2562-2639",
      "markText": "中国人受过苦，因此我尤其希望中国人能够尽量帮助穷而无告者，帮助天下那些受尽了冤、吃尽了苦的穷人，使他们能够理解自身所应拥有的权利，及其将来可能的发展方向。",
      "totalCount": 252,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300124900&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=2562&rangeEnd=2639",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/b4c320a0813ab974ag010e05?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=2562&rangeEnd=2639"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300124900_4_1754-1786",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "1754-1786",
      "markText": "许先生说，所有对历史的观照，最终都是为了帮助我们更好地看见未来。",
      "totalCount": 238,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300124900&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=1754&rangeEnd=1786",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/b4c320a0813ab974ag010e05?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=1754&rangeEnd=1786"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300124900_5_2384-2429",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "2384-2429",
      "markText": "只有相信自己的良心，我们才会平心静气地去对待他者，不卑不亢，与他者建立平等互惠的长久关系。",
      "totalCount": 238,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300124900&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=2384&rangeEnd=2429",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/b4c320a0813ab974ag010e05?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=2384&rangeEnd=2429"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300124900_4_557-586",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "557-586",
      "markText": "他说：首先要胸襟广大，所有人类走过的路，都是我走过的路之一",
      "totalCount": 234,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300124900&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=557&rangeEnd=586",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/b4c320a0813ab974ag010e05?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=557&rangeEnd=586"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300124900_17_23407-23467",
      "chapterUid": 17,
      "range": "23407-23467",
      "markText": "我给年轻人的忠告是，要做个了解自己、同情别人的人。了解自己的短处，佩服人家的长处，这种人生态度会赢得许多意料不到的朋友。",
      "totalCount": 234,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300124900&chapterUid=17&rangeStart=23407&rangeEnd=23467",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/b4c320a0813ab974ag010e05?chapterUid=17&rangeStart=23407&rangeEnd=23467"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300124900_13_1015-1097",
      "chapterUid": 13,
      "range": "1015-1097",
      "markText": "人类能够相聚在一起，成就一番事业，是靠人与人的合作，不是靠人与人的冲突，更不是靠人剥削人。错误的时代是“我征服我的敌人，我毁掉我的敌人”，未来的时代是成全每一个人。",
      "totalCount": 228,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300124900&chapterUid=13&rangeStart=1015&rangeEnd=1097",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/b4c320a0813ab974ag010e05?chapterUid=13&rangeStart=1015&rangeEnd=1097"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300124900_11_3452-3500",
      "chapterUid": 11,
      "range": "3452-3500",
      "markText": "首先，中国不一定会屈服；其次，中国单靠内需、内销，即可维持一个相当大的平衡体，自己关起门过日子。",
      "totalCount": 224,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300124900&chapterUid=11&rangeStart=3452&rangeEnd=3500",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/b4c320a0813ab974ag010e05?chapterUid=11&rangeStart=3452&rangeEnd=3500"
    },
    {
